snippet.title: Obhabe keno | Bela seshe Video Song 1 | Anupam Roy | 2015 New Bengali Song

localized.description:
For the latest 'BELASESHE' updates, Join Us On
https://www.facebook.com/Belasesheben...
Director Nandita Roy and Shiboprosad Mukherjee's newest venture Belaseshe. Hitting studios this May.

Obhabe keno:
From the movie Belaseshe - In the Autumn of My Life, a Nandita Roy and Shiboprosad Mukherjee Film. Singer: Anupam Roy. Lyrics and Music: Anupam Roy. A song of detachment between lovers of yesteryears who have lost their way in the monotony of life. While the habit of each other alienates, love takes a back seat.
Obhabe keno: Singer: Anupam Roy. Lyrics and Music: Anupam Roy | Guitar: Rhythm Shaw | Flute: Bubai | Mixing and Mastering: Shomi Chatterjee and Srirup Chatterjee.
